These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, thai, turkish, russian
4 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, cat, fish
1. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the australian##1
3. the thai is on the left or right of the turkish##3
4. the russian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
5. the russian is not to the left of the owner of the fish##8
6. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
7. the thai is somewhere between the australian and the owner of the bird##7
8. the thai and the owner of the fish have the same parity positions##9
9. the turkish and the owner of the lizard have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | australian | thai | turkish     | russian |
| Pet           | cat   | fish     | bird | lizard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, gardening, cooking, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person drinking hot-chocolate have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
4. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
5. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
8. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite     | lemonade    | mirinda | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby      | baking | gardening | cooking      | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, lemonade, juice
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapes, plum, broccoli
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
2. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
7. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the person eating grapes##8
8. the person drinking sprite and the person eating grapes have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | sprite    | lemonade   | 7up    | juice  |
| Food       | grapes | broccoli | garlic | plum |

