.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, mechanic, journalist, engineer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, folk, gospel, d&b
1. the fan techno is the mechanic##1
2. the fan folk is on the right of the fan gospel##1
3. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
4. the fan d&b is on the left or right of the journalist##3
5. the fan folk is on the left of the electrician##1
6. the engineer and the fan d&b have the same parity positions##9
7. the journalist is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | engineer | journalist | electrician  | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | gospel             | folk          | d&b | techno    |

