.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, funk, ambient, indie
4 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, snake, guinea-pig
1. the fan ambient is not the owner of the snake##6
2. the owner of the ferret and the fan metal have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the lizard and the fan funk have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the fan ambient##5
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the fan indie##1
6. the fan funk is not the owner of the lizard##6
7. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the fan funk##5
8. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the fan metal##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the fan indie##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal | ambient | indie  | funk |
| Pet           | lizard   | ferret     | snake | guinea-pig      |

