.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, radish, kale, pumpkin
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
2. the person eating pumpkin and the person driving the taxi have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
4. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
5. the person eating radish is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the taxi##7
6. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | kale | cranberry   | radish | pumpkin |
| Transport   | bike   | airplane | skateboard    | taxi      |

