2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating pear##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating banana##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person eating tomato have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
