.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, papaya, spinach, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, british, chinese, nigerian
1. the person eating avocado is not the nigerian##6
2. the nigerian is not to the right of the malaysian##8
3. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
4. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
5. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the chinese##3
6. the nigerian is on the far left##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
8. the person eating pineapple is the british##1
9. the person eating avocado and the malaysian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | papaya   | avocado    | spinach | pineapple    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | malaysian | chinese   | british |

