2. the fan rock is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
3. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the fan metal and the fan rock##7
4. the fan rock is somewhere between the fan country and the person eating artichoke##7
5. the fan jazz is not the person eating spinach##6
6. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating radish is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
