.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, coffee, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, thriller, horror
1. the person watching epic movies is not the person drinking cola##6
2. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
8. the person watching epic movies and the person drinking 7up have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching thriller movies and the person drinking coffee have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | cola   | hot-chocolate  | coffee  | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | thriller | horror | epic      |

