.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, tea, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, funk, hip-hop, punk
 1. the person drinking iced-tea and the fan hip-hop have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 3. the fan disco is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking juice##7
 4. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan hip-hop is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 7. the person drinking cola and the fan funk have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan punk##3
 9. the fan punk is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan disco##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | juice  | cola | tea  | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | punk | hip-hop     | disco | funk     |

