.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, almond-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, gardening, cooking
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 6. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 7. the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is video-games have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 9. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is video-games have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | almond-milk        | sprite   | 7up      |
| Hobby      | cooking | gardening | video-games | rock-climbing |

 